---
import StoryLayout from '../../layouts/StoryLayout.astro';
import stories from '../../data/stories.json';

const story = stories.find(s => s.slug === 'mercor-data-breach')!;
---

<style is:global>
  /* --- Canvas --- */
  .phantom-wrap { width: 100%; margin: 0; line-height: 0; }
  .mercor-data-breach-canvas { display: block; width: 100%; height: 380px; background: var(--bg); }
  .canvas-note { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); text-align: center; margin: 0.6rem 0 0; padding: 0 1rem; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* --- Reenactment 1: The Stack --- */
  .mercor-stack-wrap {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 28px 24px 20px;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
  }
  .mercor-stack-layer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .mercor-stack-top {
    background: rgba(232,232,232,0.04);
    color: var(--muted);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .mercor-stack-top span { opacity: 0.7; }
  .mercor-stack-mid {
    background: rgba(168,85,247,0.12);
    color: var(--story);
    border: 1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.25);
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .mercor-stack-bottom {
    background: rgba(232,232,232,0.03);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(100px, 1fr));
    gap: 6px;
    padding: 12px;
  }
  .mercor-stack-avatar {
    background: rgba(232,232,232,0.05);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 6px 8px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .mercor-stack-avatar.mercor-stack-highlighted {
    border-color: rgba(168,85,247,0.4);
    color: var(--story);
  }
  .mercor-stack-arrow {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding: 6px 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .mercor-stack-arrow span { opacity: 0.6; }
  .mercor-stack-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* --- Reenactment 2: The Install --- */
  .mercor-install-wrap {
    background: #0a0a0a;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
  }
  .mercor-install-header {
    background: rgba(232,232,232,0.04);
    padding: 8px 14px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .mercor-install-body {
    padding: 16px 18px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .mercor-install-cmd { color: var(--text); }
  .mercor-install-output { color: var(--muted); }
  .mercor-install-success {
    color: var(--story);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 14px;
  }
  .mercor-install-success::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 4px;
    height: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--story);
    box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--story);
  }
  .mercor-install-note {
    padding: 10px 18px 14px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* --- Reenactment 3: The File --- */
  .mercor-file-wrap {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, monospace;
  }
  .mercor-file-header {
    background: rgba(232,232,232,0.04);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .mercor-file-body { padding: 16px 18px; }
  .mercor-file-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 5px 0;
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,42,42,0.4);
  }
  .mercor-file-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .mercor-file-key {
    color: var(--muted);
    min-width: 200px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .mercor-file-val { color: var(--text); }
  .mercor-file-val.mercor-file-redacted {
    background: rgba(232,232,232,0.08);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 0 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  .mercor-file-val.mercor-file-attached {
    color: var(--story);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .mercor-file-footer {
    padding: 10px 18px 14px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .mercor-file-row { flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
    .mercor-file-key { min-width: 0; }
  }
</style>

<StoryLayout story={story}>
  <div class="container">

<section class="section" id="layer">
  <h2><span class="num">01 — The Layer Beneath the Lab</span>The Quiet Tier the Public Never Sees</h2>
  <p>On April 7, 2026, Anthropic announced a restricted research model called Claude Mythos. It was not publicly accessible. It was not listed in Anthropic's API documentation. Within roughly twenty-four hours of that announcement, accounts that had no authorization began querying it — a fact Bloomberg would report two weeks later, on April 21.</p>
  <p>The intruders had not broken into Anthropic. According to Bloomberg and Tom's Hardware, reporting independently, they had read something already in the wild — knowledge of Anthropic's internal file-system naming conventions, extracted from a different company's data breach the week before — and used it to find Mythos before the rest of the internet knew where to look. Anthropic confirmed it was investigating "a report claiming unauthorised access to Claude Mythos Preview through one of our third-party vendor environments."</p>
  <p>The other company was Mercor.</p>
  <p>Most people who follow AI have never heard of Mercor. It does not build models. It builds the layer the models are built on. Founded in 2023 by Brendan Foody, Adarsh Hiremath, and Surya Midha — three Thiel Fellows out of Bellarmine College Prep in San Jose — Mercor recruits subject-matter experts and pays them to teach AI systems how to think. Attorneys evaluate legal reasoning. Cardiologists grade diagnostic outputs. Machine-learning engineers write the tasks a model is then trained to solve. Some sit for recorded video interviews about specialized work. The contractors are the curriculum.</p>
  <p>By October 2025, the company had raised $350 million in a Series C led by Felicis Ventures, reaching a $10 billion valuation. It managed approximately 30,000 contractors, according to TechCrunch and Wikipedia, paying out more than $1.5 million per day. According to The Information, citing a person familiar with the matter, annualized revenue exceeded $1 billion. Mercor's reported clients included Meta, Anthropic, OpenAI, and Google. Its headquarters occupied space at 181 Fremont in San Francisco — a block from the Salesforce Tower, a neighborhood dense with the companies whose models depend on what Mercor's contractors produce.</p>
  <p>The public never sees this layer. Foundation models are trained on the open internet, then refined on what humans judge to be good. The humans doing the judging are not employees of the labs. They are contractors, managed by intermediaries, working from laptops in dozens of countries, submitting feedback that shapes the model's personality, its clinical instincts, its legal reasoning. Mercor is one of the largest aggregators of those humans. When it was breached, the breach did not stop at the contractors' personal data. It reached upward, into the labs themselves.</p>

